    description: "The Concepts x Nike SB Dunk Low “Orange Lobster - Special Box” is a limited edition collaboration between the Boston based sneaker boutique and Nike SB on the skate shoe that continues its popular “Lobster” series. Introduced by Concepts and Nike SB in 2008, the “Lobster” collection is a nod to Concepts’ Boston area roots and its cuisine. The series has featured several iconic SB Dunks, including the “Red Lobster,” “Blue Lobster,” “Green Lobster,” “Yellow Lobster,” “Purple Lobster,” and now the “Orange Lobster.” Similar to previous colorways in the line, the “Orange Lobster” features a tonal design, this time in orange. A black rubber band appears on the forefoot as a reference to the bands that keep a lobster’s claws closed. A white and orange picnic blanket inspired checkerboard pattern is found on the interior lining. Please note: this is the listing for the version of the Concepts x Nike SB Dunk Low “Orange Lobster” that comes with special, more-limited packaging. Release date: December 2, 2022",
