    color: "",
    description: "The SB Dunk Low \"Copperhead,\" designed in collaboration with pro skater Dashawn Jordan, features a premium black suede base distinguished by realistic snakeskin-textured overlays in a muted earth tone. This predatory aesthetic is sharply elevated by a vibrant \"Action Grape\" purple inner lining and a \"Teal\" heel tab, providing a high-contrast strike to the dark profile. A specialized copper-finished lace dubrae sits at the base of the throat as a nod to the shoe’s reptilian namesake, while the tonal black midsole and Swoosh maintain a stealthy, performance-ready foundation. Grounded by a durable rubber outsole and Zoom Air cushioning in the sockliner, this release successfully pairs raw street style with the technical requirements of elite skateboarding.",
