    color: "",
    description: "The Supreme x Nike SB Dunk High \"Rammellzee\" is a collaboration by the legendary streetwear brand on a colorway the retro skate shoe that salutes New York based visual artist Rammellzee. Supreme’s ties to Rammellzee date back to at least 2006 when the Queens, New York native appeared in a short promotional video for the “World Famous” brand. Supreme honors the artist on the SB Dunk High by featuring his abstract artwork on the upper’s canvas toe, mid-panel, and heel. Grey suede overlays appear throughout the design and on the Swoosh. The gold “Supreme” lace dubrae harkens back to the detailing found on Supreme’s early Nike SB collaborations from the 2000s. Release date: August 31, 2023",
