    color: "",
    description: "The Nike Air Max 95 NDSTRKT “Black/Reflective” gives a rugged update to the ever-popular retro running shoe. A seminal model in Nike’s Air Max collection, the Air Max 95 is recast as a boot-like sneaker under the NDSTRKT (pronounced “Indestruct”) moniker. The design incorporates rubberized overlay panels, reinforced mesh, and leather, all new modifications to the design of the Air Max 95 that are built to last. The rubber overlays come into play along the mid-panel, on the toe, and on the heel. Silver reflective lace straps assist in supporting the lacing system and extend from the eyelets to the black rubber midsole. A stealthy black Swoosh is embroidered onto the heel and the model’s original split Air Max logo is stitched onto the black tongue. Underfoot, the Air Max 95 NDSTRKT retains the look of the original Air Max 95’s visible Air units in the forefoot and heel. Release date: February 15, 2021.",
