    color: "",
    description: "The Nike Dunk Low TD “Black/White” is the toddler sizing of a timeless two-tone colorway of the low-top shoe that was released in March 2021. In 2020, the Dunk made a triumphant return after spending several years tucked away in the vault. Collaborations with a who’s-who of fashion designers, music artists, and more were released in conjunction with returning original colorways to help spark a renewed interest in the venerable silhouette. The “Black/White” speaks to the shoe’s enduring retro style that feels fresher than ever in the present day. Black leather overlays on the forefoot, eyelets, collar, and heel contrast the upper’s white leather base. The same black leather detailing can be found on the Swoosh branding and white “Nike” embroidery on the heel. A black nylon branding tag with a “Nike” logo stitched on the white mesh tongue finishes off the look. Release date: March 10, 2021.",
