    color: "",
    description: "The Nike Air VaporMax Plus “Triple White” combines the design language of Nike’s Air Max Plus and Air VaporMax into one progressively-styled silhouette. Undeniably comfortable, the Air VaporMax Plus is cast in an all-white synthetic nubuck and neoprene construction. Tonal glossy TPU overlays on both sides assist in supporting the lacing structure. A Pure Platinum Swoosh appears on the collar and an Air Max Plus-inspired “Vm Air” emblem can be found on the heel. Tonal “Nike” insignia appears on the white tongue tag as a continuation of the model’s monochromatic white aesthetic. Nike finishes the look off with full-length visible VaporMax Air bubbles beneath the white midsole. Release date: February 9, 2018.",
