    color: "",
    description: "The Zoom Kobe 6 GS \"3D\" delivers a clinical, high-octane revival of the 2011 fan-favorite, masterfully blending Kobe Bryant’s \"Black Mamba\" technicality with a radical, optical-illusion aesthetic. This iteration features a premium micro-mesh upper covered in the silhouette’s signature raised polyurethane \"snakeskin\" islands, utilized here in an alternating Red and Blue \"3D\" pattern that provides a vibrating, multi-dimensional strike to the profile. The design is defined by its anatomical strike, utilizing a specialized glass-reinforced TPU heel counter in glossy red and a sleek \"Dark Grey\" midsole. Grounded by a high-traction translucent outsole and finished with mismatched branding on the tongue, this release successfully pairs the Kobe 6's elite performance DNA with a playful, archival colorway that remains a staple of basketball culture.",
