    description: "The Nike Air More Uptempo \"Industrial Blue\" is a colorway of Scottie Pippen’s retro basketball shoe with head-turning blue branding. The Air More Uptempo was worn by Pippen with the Chicago Bulls in 1996 and today, the model is beloved for its unique, ‘90s-inspired styling, ties to Pippen, and for its eye-catching colorways. The shoe has a White Bone leather upper with Industrial Blue leather “AIR” detailing on either side. The blue hue also appears on the Swoosh on the toe and on the heel. Small visible Air cushioning bubbles in the midsole complete the look. Release date: June 10, 2023",
